reviews.review_text: the burp wow! check out the burp in the intro into aiko!!!!!!!!!!!!
Urrrrp! Yep, that was a belch. $.50 says it was Phil.

best part of the show..sad worst show I saw in 104.

The belch was the recorded stuff they did before the Greeks. 

Pretty damn sure it was Phil!

Hmmmm While I saw some shows in 1992 that were definitely worse than this one, this one has a turgid set list in a year of sparkling set lists. First is actually rather well played but short. 2nd settles into a mellow mediocrity with a nice D>S. Obviously someone told them they needed to step up on night 3

Phase The two channels of the main source are 180 degrees out of phase.  One side needs to be inverted.
Except of course for the patches, they are fine.
